The Hairdresser's Husband;;1990;;R;;Comedy,Drama,Romance;;7.3;;Patrice Leconte;;Jean Rochefort,Anna Galiena,Roland Bertin,Maurice Chevit,Philippe Clévenot,Jacques Mathou,Claude Aufaure,Albert Delpy,Henry Hocking,Ticky Holgado,Michèle Laroque,Anne-Marie Pisani,Pierre Meyrand,Yveline Ailhaud,Julien Bukowski,Youssef Hamid,Laurence Ragon,Arlette Tephany;;Twelve-year-old Antoine falls profoundly in love with a voluptuous but suicidal hairdresser, a formative experience he never forgets. Much later in life, he seeks to repeat his romance by marrying Mathilde - also voluptuous and also a hairdresser - with whom he forms an intimate and consuming relationship in an attempt to blot out the miseries of this world from their lives.;;https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0100112/